  §3: Full β-function system + SO(10) coupling constants (C_i=0.5)
  §4: Numerical integration protocol (RK45, runbook)
  §5: Theorem 1 (gauge-RG-flow-to-SM-CONDITIONAL) with H1-H5
  §6: Devil's-advocate audit (3 objections, CLAUDE.md §6.3.1)

[Code] Codes/supplementary/Math75_Q2_RG_integration.py (v1.0)
  - beta_i_TECT() now implements full BCC-defect contribution
  - Formula: β_i^{TECT} = n_d*α_i^2*(C_i/16π²)*(q_0*a_BCC)²
  - C_1=C_2=C_3=0.5 (SO(10) symmetry, Lemma 1)
  - Output JSON: status classification (FALSIFIED|PARTIAL|SUCCESS)
  - Pre-registered gates: |Δα_i|>5% / [0.5%-5%] / <0.5%

[Code] Docs/manual/CODE_MANUAL.md
  - Entry for Math75_Q2_RG_integration.py v1.0 [ACTIVE]

[Changelog] CHANGELOG.md
  - New Math75-Q2-Addendum-A-RGE-completion entry (2026-04-24)

[Scope] Turn 6 Track B, Task #92, Pillar 4 Q2 closure (Math86 roadmap)
